---
title: Smoke Test Recipe
tags:
  - test
servings: 1
time:
  prep: 5 minutes
  cook: 15 minutes
difficulty: easy
---

Heat @oil{1%tbsp} in #pan{} over medium heat.

Add @onion{1%small}(diced) and sauté for ~sauté onion{3%minutes} until softened.

Add @garlic{2%cloves}(minced) and cook for ~cook garlic{30%seconds}.

Add @tomatoes{1%can} and simmer for ~simmer{10%minutes}.

Let rest for ~rest{2%minutes} before serving.